# The WhatsApp Business number every CTA on the site opens.
# E.164 digits only — no "+", no spaces. e.g. 923001234567
# REQUIRED: the production build fails without it, because an unset value
# produces https://wa.me/?text=… — a link that opens WhatsApp with no recipient
# and silently loses every enquiry.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WA_NUMBER=
